{"tid":2164624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"三峽水庫將遇修壩以來最大洪峯 重慶多處景點被淹","createTime":"2020-08-19T09:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:23:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc479a1081d96b293e02050c24438b3ea9ddc30","tid":2164624,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200819/FUBZFEA45RG6JHTFK5GXN6BYQ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200819%2FFUBZFEA45RG6JHTFK5GXN6BYQ4%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=07490e3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200819%2FFUBZFEA45RG6JHTFK5GXN6BYQ4%2F&h=2fa312fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200819/FUBZFEA45RG6JHTFK5GXN6BYQ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n長江2020年第5號洪水前日（17日）在長江上游形成。今早（19日），5號洪水的洪峯開始進入三峽水庫，預計最大入庫流量在每秒74,000立方米左右。這也將是三峽大壩修建以來遇到的最大洪峯。三峽水庫自2002年開始下閘蓄水以來，入庫最大洪峯為2012年71,200立方米/秒。<br />\n<br />\n甘肅省紅十字會今日透露，8月上旬以來，甘肅隴南、定西、慶陽、平涼、天水等地大範圍下雨，局部地區出現大到暴雨，引發洪澇、暴洪災害。截至目前，災害共造成3人死亡，13個縣區116個鄉鎮632個村120,547人受災，直接經濟損失約3.4億元人民幣（約3.8億港元）。"},{"pid":"f3dcd6c5b7c01aebaab2fc3b84ba1f41f8090e56","tid":2164624,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a499b23869fce45a3bb7f1e6a6135a3bdae1bd","tid":2164624,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下游城巿鄉村全面小康"},{"pid":"37a9f9edb6a04aa0e2b99897e021a877dfba80aa","tid":2164624,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}